//For renewal orders, ICOMS alters service occurrences, resulting in duplicate old services remaining active in BSSN. 
//We utilize the dataset below to compare and mark outdated records as Disconnected during the final upsert.

// 1) Build reference lists, ignoring nulls and de-duping.
